heorie innerhalb von Davidsons semantischem Programm spricht.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 28. Feb 2023) 0aAnalysis (Philosophy). 0aSemantics (Philosophy). 4aDonald Davidson. 4aErkenntnistheorie. 4aPhilosophie. 4aWahrheitstheorie. 7aPHILOSOPHY / Criticism.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Philosophy 2000 - 2014z9783110636949oZDB-23-GPH08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruyterteBook Paket De Gruyter Ontos 2002-2012z9783110331219oZDB-23-DON0 cprintz978311032390040uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311032426640uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110324266423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110324266/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DONc2002d2012  aZDB-23-GPHc2000d2014